# CLAUDE.md - Moji Integration Example

This is an example of how to integrate Moji into your project's CLAUDE.md file.

---

## Project: My Awesome App

### Session Personality

When starting a new session, greet with wisdom:

```
/moji flex --creature claude
```

### Celebrations

When completing a major milestone:

```
/moji banner "SHIPPED"
```

When tests pass:

```
/moji say "All tests green!" --creature tux
```

### Documentation Style

Use moji for README headers:

```
/moji header "Installation"
/moji header "Usage"
/moji header "API Reference"
```

Use dividers between sections:

```
/moji divider --style fancy
```

### Commit Messages

Follow gitmoji convention:

```
/moji commit
```

