## Quick Reference

```
/moji banner <text>           ASCII art text
/moji fortune                 Random wisdom
/moji say <text>              Creature speech
/moji emoji <search>          Find emojis
/moji commit                  Gitmoji list
/moji flex                    Fortune + creature
/moji divider                 Section divider
/moji box <text>              Boxed text
/moji header <text>           File header
/moji rainbow <text>          Colored text
```

